#message:05:000
{
	[Style Right]
	Hey, buddy![BR]
	[Pause 10]Do you think you could do me a[BR]
	solid and get rid of that rock?[BR]
	[Wait][Next]
	We got a schedule to maintain,[BR]
	ya know![BR]
	[Pause 10]If you can't help,[PrintRising] then go away.[BR]
	[Pause 5]We don't need you![/fx][Wait][End]
}

#message:05:001
{
	[Style Right]
	You're a legend for blowing[BR]
	up that rock.[BR]
	[Pause 20]But [Pause 3][PrintRising]hey![/fx] [Pause 5][PrintRising]No funny business![BR]
	Keep that Bob-Omb in check![/fx][BR]
	[Wait][Next]
	[Pause 10]We're going to [SaveColor][Color:21]Mt. Rugged[RestoreColor] in a[BR]
	minute here.[BR]
	Either ya get on or you screw[BR]
	off, got that?[BR]
	[Yield][End]
}

#message:05:002
{
	[Style Right]
	[PrintRising]Ay, buddy.[/fx][BR]
	[Pause 10]We're going to [SaveColor][Color:21]Mt. Rugged[RestoreColor] in a[BR]
