}

#message:05:003
{
	[Next]
	[PrintRising]Pack your bags, folks![BR]
	[Shake]Chop chop! We're leaving![/fx][Wait][End]
}

#message:05:004
{
	[Next]
	Don't come back![Wait][End]
}

#message:05:005
{
	[Style Right]
	Kinoko Town![BR]
	[Pause 15]Kinoko Town![BR]
	[DelayOff][Pause 5]Get your butts off the train![Wait][End]
}

#message:05:006
{
	[Style Right]
	Hey, buddy.[Pause 5][BR]
	Have you ever heard of a[BR]
	"schedule"?[BR]
	[Wait][Next]
	Well even the train's got one,[Pause 5][BR]
	so be patient and talk about[BR]
	peak fiction or something.[Wait][End]
}

#message:05:007
{
	[Style Right]
	Shy Guys must have gotten their[BR]
	ears chopped off or something,[Pause 3][BR]
	because[Pause 5][PrintRising] heck,[Pause 5] they won't listen[BR]
	to me at all[/fx]![BR]
	[Wait][Next]
	At this point I could just run[BR]
	the Shy Guy over, but that might[BR]
	raise the game's age rating, [Pause 5]so[BR]
	I wanna play it safe.[Wait][End]
}

#message:05:008
{
	[Style Right]
	Boy, the kinds of stupid people I[BR]
	have to tolerate on a daily basis.[BR]
	[Pause 20]Anyways we're leaving soon.[BR]
	You getting on or nah?[BR]
	[Yield][End]
}

#message:05:009
{
	[Style Right]
	[BR]
	[PrintRising]That's it! That's it![BR]
	[Pause 10]Move out the way![Wait][End]
}

#message:05:00A
{
	[Style Right]
	It's a shame we don't have a[BR]
	more robust transit system.[BR]
	[Pause 10]Mt. Rugged is cool for hiking[BR]
	and all but...[BR]
	[Wait][Next]
	Why can't the train take me[BR]
	some other places like...[BR]
	[Pause 15]I don't know...[BR]
	[Wait][Next]
	[SaveColor][Color:03]Gusty Gulch[RestoreColor] could be cool I[BR]
	guess? [Pause 10]Or maybe[SaveColor][Color:0D] Shiver City[RestoreColor]?[Wait][End]
}

#message:05:00B
{
	[Style Right]
	Looking at Kinoko Maps, it also[BR]
	shows there's a place called [BR]
	[SaveColor][Color:07]Loveydovey Island[RestoreColor] to the south.[BR]
	[Wait][Next]
	Building a railway system all[BR]
	the way across the sea sounds[BR]
	like a tough endeavor.[BR]
	[Wait][Next]
	If the railroad business needs[BR]
	funding to make it happen, I'm[BR]
	all for it![Wait][End]
}

#message:05:00C
{
	[Style Right]
	Yo, get this.[Pause 10][BR]
	I just saw a smoking hot maid[BR]
	the other day.[BR]
	[Wait][Next]
	It kinda looked like she had[BR]
	a shark tail though.[BR]
	[Pause 10][Wave]Weird...[/fx][BR]
	[Wait][Next]
	Can maids even have tails?[Wait][End]
}

