{
	Unused
}

#message:05:00E
{
	[Style Right]
	Why are we always getting[BR]
	the weird ones?[Pause 10][BR]
	Why not some hot Shy Gal trying[BR]
	to distract me from work?[BR]
	[Wait][Next]
	At least if I see some bosoms[BR]
	in my face, it'd give me an[BR]
	excuse to go to the bathroom.[Wait][End]
}

#message:05:00F
{
	[Style Right]
	I love trains![BR]
	I love trains![BR]
	[Wait][Next]
	Train engineering is so totally[BR]
	awesome![BR]
	[Pause 10]It's my entire passion and[BR]
	personality honestly![BR]
	[Wait][Next]
	Nothing wrong with that, right?[Wait][End]
}

#message:05:010
{
	[Style Right]
	I'm too poor to afford the train.[BR]
	[Pause 10]This makes me mad![BR]
	[Wait][Next]
	I wanna get out there and meet[BR]
	all kinds of women, but I can't[BR]
	if I'm too broke![Wait][End]
}

#message:05:011
{
	[Style Right]
	[PrintGrowing]Keep this a secret, but...[BR]
	[pause 10][Volume percent=30]I'd love to go on a date with[BR]
	a cute girl conductor.[/fx][BR]
	[Wait][Next]
	[Volume percent=100]I just love trains (and women)[BR]
	that much. Can you blame me?[Wait][End]
}

#message:05:012
{
	[Style Right]
	I'm feeling a little depressed[BR]
	lately...[BR]
