	[Wait][Next]
	It's all that Bower's fault.[BR]
	[Pause 15]Nobody else seems to notice it[BR]
	but me, [Pause 5]but I can feel his deadly[BR]
	influence everywhere I go.[BR]
	[Wait][Next]
	It's like a cursed sixth sense[BR]
	or something.[Wait][End]
}

