#message:05:017
{
	[Style Right]
	Hey, Mr. Granola.[BR]
	I got some great advice for you[BR]
	and that Goomba bud o' yours.[BR]
	[Wait][Next]
	Whenever you're staring death[BR]
	in the face, swallow your fears[BR]
	and just press [B]![BR]
	[Wait][Next]
	Don't know what I mean?[Pause 15][BR]
	Well, sometimes you COULD have[BR]
	been dead right then and there...[BR]
	[Wait][Next]
	But that good old [B] button[BR]
	friend actually saved ya.[Pause 20][BR]
	Thank me later.[Wait][End]
}

