#message:05:01D
{
	[Style Right]
	Some weird guy came up to me[BR]
	the other day and he asked if[BR]
	I wanted to join his schoolhouse.[BR]
	[Wait][Next]
	Naturally I was like, "Sure?"[BR]
	[Pause 10][Shake]Worst mistake I could have[BR]
	ever made![/fx][BR]
	[Wait][Next]
	It was actual hell![BR]
	The schoolhouse was filled with[BR]
	more horror than I could ever[BR]
	imagine.[BR]
	[Wait][Next]
	He even made me solve math[BR]
	problems! Oh God![BR]
	[Wait][Next]
	Yep... [Pause 5]never doing that again.[BR]
	[Pause 10]Don't take offers from[BR]
	strangers, kids.[Wait][End]
}

