#message:05:01F
{
	[Style Right]
	I love shopping. [Pause 5]So much fun.[BR]
	[Pause 10]One day I'd like to visit some[BR]
	other towns and see what their[BR]
	malls are like.[BR]
	[Wait][Next]
	Like [SaveColor][Color:1D]Coconut Mall[RestoreColor].[BR]
	[Pause 8]That's a good one to go to.[BR]
	[Pause 20]Well, except for the fact that[BR]
	there's been some bad reviews.[BR]
	[Wait][Next]
	Lately, Shy Guys were doing[BR]
	donuts in the parking lot.[BR]
	[Pause 10]Not exactly the mall's fault,[BR]
	[Pause 3]more so on security.[BR]
	[Wait][Next]
	Still, how could I say no to[BR]
	the most popular shopping mall?[Wait][End]
}

#message:05:020
{
	[Style Right]
	I adore shopping. [Pause 5]Tons of fun.[BR]
	[Pause 10]Some day I'd love to visit some[BR]
	other cities and see what their[BR]
	malls are like, ya know?[BR]
	[Wait][Next]
	[PrintRising]Oooo! Like [SaveColor][Color:1D]Coconut Mall[RestoreColor].[/fx][BR]
	[Pause 8]Can't go wrong with there.[BR]
	[Pause 20]Ummm... [Pause 5]'cept for the recent[BR]
	negative reception.[BR]
	[Wait][Next]
	They caught Shy Guys doing[BR]
	donuts in the parking lot.[BR]
	[Pause 10]That's on security for not[BR]
	doing their job though.[BR]
	[Wait][Next]
	Still, I couldn't say no to such[BR]
	a popular mall![Wait][End]
}

